Mojo templates Syntax file
Language: Mojo templates
By yko <ykorshak@gmail.com>

DESCRIPTION

Syntax file for highlighting embedded Perl code in Mojo templates.
Designed to highlight syntax of both html.ep and html.epl formats.

INSTALLATION

Save this files into your ~/.vim/ directory.

CONFIGURATION

Configurations variables:

    :let mojo_disable_html = 1

For highlight embedded Perl code in __DATA__ sections of your Perl files,
add following line to your .vimrc:

    autocmd FileType perl syn include @perlDATA syntax/MojoliciousTemplate.vim

